complianceText:
The output format does not fully comply with the desired format specified in the description. The expected output format requires the values to be in the format of `<comma_separated_list_of_items>`, but some of the fields are using `-||-` to indicate absence of items (e.g., "People names" and "Specific topics"). Additionally, "General themes" does not use the `<comma_separated_list_of_items>` format, though it only contains one item. The output should adhere strictly to the format specified in the description.
